(22, 'Lut  GDH cn quy nh c  th hn  p dng vo thc tin ngay', 'lut-gdh-cn-quy-nh-c-th-hn--ap-dng-vao-thc-tin-ngay', '', '<div id="detail-content">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>(GD&T) - Chiu 14-11, Quc hi tho lun ti hi trng v d tho Lut Gio dc i hc (GDH). Cc i biu u th hin s tn thnh c bn vi ni dung d tho. Tuy nhin, theo nhiu i biu,  lut nhanh i vo cuc sng, iu chnh hiu qu gio dc i hc, lut cn quy nh c th hn, hn ch thp nht vic giao Chnh ph v B Gio dc v o to quy nh, hng dn</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 400px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images596537_141111.jpg" alt="i biu Nguyn Th Kim B (on Kin Giang) pht biu  kin. nh: Internet" height="278" width="400" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">i biu Nguyn Th Kim B (on Kin Giang) pht biu  kin</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Lut phi gii quyt vn  c bn</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ti bui tho lut, cc i biu u th hin s ng tnh vi vic cn thit ban hnh Lut GDH  th ch ha cc ch trng, chnh sch ca ng v Nh nc v i mi v pht trin GDH; to hnh lang php l thun li v thng nht  iu chnh ton din cc vn  lin quan n GDH, gp phn i mi cn bn v ton din GDH Vit Nam nhm nng cao cht lng o to, pht trin ngun nhn lc p ng yu cu xy dng v bo v t quc trong thi k i mi v hi nhp quc t.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">i biu Nguyn Th Kim B (on Kin Giang) khng nh s cn thit ban hnh lut v hin nay cc quy nh cn thiu, chung chung nn cha to iu kin tt nht cho GDH. S cn thit  cng i hi d tho lut GDH cn c th, trnh chung chung. Tuy nhin, qua nghin cu, d tho lut cn c mt s quy nh chung chung, giao cho Chnh ph v B Gio dc v o to. Do vy, cn r sot  quy nh c th hn, hn ch giao Chnh ph v B Gio dc v o to quy nh v hng dn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cng quan im vi i biu B, i biu H Th Thy (on Vnh Phc) cho rng, lut cn quy nh c th hn, khng nn quy nh mt cch khi qut. Tm huyt vi GDH, i biu L Vn Hc (on Lm ng) nhn mnh: Lut khng tham vng gii quyt tt c cc vn  lin quan n GDH ni chung, nhng phi gii quyt vn  c bn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Nng cao cht lng o to i hc</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Mt trong nhng nguyn nhn khin GDH cha t cht lng cao trong thi gian va qua l do i ng gio vin cn thiu v yu. i biu Nguyn Th Hi (on Ngh An) phn tch: mt tn ti ln GDH l s lng trng, sinh vin khng ngng tng, nhng i ng nh gio va thiu va cha p ng c yu cu. Trong khi , c tnh trng mt thy dy ti 4-5 trng, phi thu tr ging cho nhng khon thi gian khng sp xp c. iu ny l thc t cn sm c bin php gii quyt, do vy d tho lut cn c mt iu khon quy nh v vn  ny. Nh mt s  kin, i biu Hi ng tnh cn quy nh trnh  chun ca ging vin phi c trnh  thc s tr ln.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vi i biu Trn Minh Diu (on Qung Bnh)  nng cao cht lng GDH cn quy hoch li mng li GDH. D tho lut cn c ch ti  mnh  c cu li mng li GDH, trnh vic m nhiu trng nh thi gian va qua.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>V Thnh</strong></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 3, 0, 8, '2011-11-15 03:49:47', 62, '', '2011-11-17 07:59:48', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-15 03:47:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 7, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 23, ''),
(23, 'i mi cn bn, ton din gio dc-o to', 'i-mi-cn-bn-toan-din-giao-dc-ao-to', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">(GD&amp;TD)- l mt trong 9 gii php c a ra ti Ngh quyt v k hoch pht trin kinh t-x hi 5 nm 2011-2015 va c Quc hi thng qua ti phin hp ton th sng nay (08/11).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;" id="detail-content">\r\n<table style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 451px; height: 101px;" class="quote center" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #3366ff;">Mc tiu tng qut cho 5 nm ti l </span><span style="color: #3366ff;">pht trin kinh t nhanh, bn vng, gn vi i mi m hnh tng trng v c cu li nn kinh t theo hng nng cao cht lng, hiu qu sc cnh tranh. Bo m phc li x hi v an sinh x hi, nng cao i sng vt cht v tinh thn ca nhn dn. Tng cng hot ng i ngoi v nng cao hiu qu hi nhp quc t. Bo v vng chc c lp, ch quyn, thng nht, ton vn lnh th, gi vng an ninh chnh tr v trt t, an ton x hi, to nn tng n nm 2020 nc ta c bn tr thnh nc cng nghip theo hng hin i.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<table style="width: 286px; float: left;" class="image rightside" align="right" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="Q" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images594178_images.jpg" height="221" width="277" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center"><span style="font-size: x-small; color: #ff6600;">Quc hi  thng qua Ngh quyt v k hoch pht trin kinh t-x hi 5 nm 2011-2015&nbsp; vi t l 89,20% i biu tn thnh</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nDi s iu khin ca Ph Ch tch Quc hi Nguyn Th Kim Ngn, Quc hi  biu quyt thng qua Ngh quyt v k hoch pht trin kinh t-x hi 5 nm 2011-2015 vi 446 tn thnh trn tng s 458 i biu tham gia (t 89,20%).\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Theo , Quc hi n nh ch s gi tiu dng (CPI) khong 5 - 7% vo 2015, GDP tng khong 6,5 - 7%, t trng u t ton x hi 5 nm khong 33,5% - 35% GDP. Trong nhng nm ti s gim dn nhp siu v phn u  mc di 10% kim ngch xut khu vo 2015.<br /> <br /> Mc tiu t l bi chi ngn sch c Quc hi thng nht  mc di 4,5% vo 2015 (c cng thm tri phiu Chnh ph). T l huy ng thu v ph vo ngn sch khng qu 22% - 23% GDP nm. N cng n 2015 khng qu 65% GDP, d n ca Chnh ph khng qu 50% GDP, d n quc gia khng qu 50% GDP.<br /> <br /> Trc , trong Bo co thm tra ca y ban Kinh t trnh ln Thng v Quc hi xem xt c  ngh mc tiu n 2015, ch s gi tiu dng bnh qun di 9%/nm, nm 2011 l 17%-18%, nm 2012 tng  mc 1 con s, nm 2013 - 2014 di 6% v nm 2015 di 5%.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> Kim sot nhp siu  mc khong 4% kim ngch xut khu v khng qu 5 t USD vo nm 2015. Bi chi ngn sch nh nc tnh theo thng l quc t v phn u di 5% vo nm 2015. T l huy ng vo ngn sch khng qu 24% GDP/nm.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table style="float: right; width: 373px; height: 519px;" class="quote center" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="margin-left: 60px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff6600;"><em><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>9 gii php  thc hin cc ch tiu:</strong><br /> <br /></span></em><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> Th nht,</strong> Khc phc nhanh, hiu qu nhng hn ch, yu km do cc nguyn nhn ch quan trong lnh o, ch o, qun l, iu hnh ca cc cp, cc ngnh.<br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> Th hai</strong>, c  n c cu li nn kinh t gn vi i mi m hnh tng trng theo hng nng cao cht lng, hiu qu v sc cnh tranh, thc hin ng b trong tt c cc ngnh, lnh vc trn phm vi c nc v tng a phng, n v c s, sn xut ch yu. Trong  cn tp trung c cu u t cng, th trng ti chnh (trng tm l h thng ngn hng thng mi, cc t chc ti chnh), doanh nghip (m trng tm l cc tp on, doanh nghip Nh nc).<br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> Th ba,</strong> tip tc kin tr kim ch lm pht, n nh kinh t v m, n nh gi tr sc mua ng tin. C cu li thu-chi ngn sch. R sot, iu chnh phn cp qun l u t t ngun Ngn sch Nh nc v tri phiu chnh ph. i mi chnh sch xut-nhp khu, kim ch nhp siu.<br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> Th t,</strong> tp trung thc hin 3 t ph, 12 nh hng chin lc pht trin Kinh t - X hi giai on 2011-2020. C bn xy dng xong h thng php lut gn vi ci cch, hon thin th ch kinh t th trng nh hng X hi ch ngha. R sot, sa i li quy nh v phn cp gia Trung ng v a phng. R sot, nh gi cc d n pht trin kt cu h tng giao thng, nht l cc vng kinh t trng im.<br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> Th nm,</strong> p dng ng b cc chnh sch, bin php pht trin kinh t gn vi pht trin vn ha, thc hin tin b v cng bng x hi, ch trng bo m an sinh x hi, gim chnh lch giu ngho.<br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> Th su,</strong> i mi cn bn, ton din Gio dc  o to, nng cao cht lng ngun nhn lc, quan tm n nhn lc lnh o. Nng cao cht lng gio dc, nht l bc i hc. Lm tt cng tc x hi ha gio dc. i mi cn bn c ch qun l Khoa hc-Cng ngh, pht trin kinh t tri thc.<br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> Th by,</strong> hon thin v nng cao hiu qu, hiu lc cc chnh sch, php lut v ti nguyn v bo v mi trng nhm bo m pht trin bn vng. Kin quyt x l cc c s gy  nhim mi trng.<br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> Th tm,</strong> tp trung xy dng, thc hin cc  n ci cch t php bo m cht lng, tin . Thc hin c hiu qu chng trnh quc gia phng chng ti phm, x l nghim cc hnh vi chng ngi thi hnh cng v. Kin quyt phng chng v x l nghim, hiu qu nn tham nhng.<br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong> Th chn,</strong> quan tm cng c quc phng, an ninh, i ngoi vng mnh, gi c lp, ch quyn, thng nht, ton vn lnh th, c bit l trn cc vng bin o ca T quc. Thc y gii quyt cc vn  tn ti v bin gii lnh th, ch trng vn  bin ng mt cch tha ng, cn bng trn nguyn tc ha bnh, tn trng php lut quc t v nguyn tc ng x khu vc.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\nN Chnh ph n nm 2015 theo  ngh ca y ban Kinh t,khng vt qu 50% GDP; n cng khng qu 60% GDP.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> Nh vy, nhiu ch tiu kinh t m y ban Kinh t ca Quc hi a ra trc  cht ch v kh khn hn so nhng ch tiu c Quc hi thng qua sng nay.<br /> <br /> n 2015, cc nhim v, gii php thc hin ti cu trc nn kinh t s gn vi i mi m hnh tng trng kinh t theo hng t ch yu pht trin theo chiu rng sang pht trin hp l gia chiu rng v chiu su.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> Trong , nhim v ti cu trc khu vc ti chnh t trng tm vo vic cng c h thng ngn hng, xem y l knh cung ng vn linh hot, thng sut cho nn kinh t; sp xp, sp nhp cc ngn hng thng mi c phn yu km v quy m nh nhm n nh th trng, hn ch ri ro cho h thng.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> Bn cnh , pht trin th trng chng khon lnh mnh, sp xp li cc cng ty chng khon, hon thin cc th ch minh bch th trng  gp phn thc y qu trnh c phn ha. Tng hiu qu hot ng cc loi hnh bo him gp phn an ton cho hot ng sn xut-kinh doanh ca nn kinh t v bo m thc hin tt chnh sch bo him x hi, bo him y t.<br /> <br /> Mt nhim v quan trng tip theo l kim sot hiu qu cc qu u t hng v thc hin cc mc tiu pht trin KT-XH, ngn chn hin tng u c lng on th trng.<br /> <br /> V ti cu trc doanh nghip nh nc, s xy dng l trnh c phn ha cc cng ty nh nc kinh doanh ngoi lnh vc sn xut kinh doanh chnh; rt dn ngun vn u t vo khu vc ti chnh (ngn hng, chng khon, bo him, qu u t), bt ng sn v chm dt vo nm 2015.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> V chnh sch ti kha, nh hng thi gian ti s tng t trng thu trc thu, gim t l tng i thu gin thu trong thu ngn sch nh nc. Trong nhng nm ti iu chnh mc thu thu nhp doanh nghip xung khong 20%, nng v m rng mc thu thu thu nhp c nhn i vi ngi c thu nhp cao.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cng trong sng nay, Quc hi tho lun  hi trng v Chng trnh mc tiu quc gia 5 nm 2011-2015; Chng trnh s dng tri phiu Chnh ph 5 nm 2011-2015.<br /> <br /> Cc i biu  tp trung tho lun v nguyn nhn tn ti, hn ch trong thc hin vn tri phiu Chnh ph giai on 2011-2015; Tng mc vn tri phiu Chnh ph giai on 2011-2015; Nguyn tc, tiu tr&nbsp; v danh mc cc d n d kin b tr vn tri phiu Chnh ph; Nguyn nhn tn ti, hn ch trong thc hin chng trnh mc tiu quc giai on 2006-2010 v nm 2011; Tng ngun vn thc hin chng trnh giai on 2011-2015; Nguyn tc, tiu tr&nbsp; v danh mc cc chng trnh mc tiu quc gia giai on 2011-2015.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Nguyn Sn</strong></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 3, 0, 8, '2011-11-15 03:51:08', 62, '', '2011-11-23 09:21:36', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-15 03:51:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 11, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 19, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(24, 'Lut GDH hng n mc tiu nng cao cht lng, hiu qu o to', 'lut-gdh-hng-n-mc-tieu-nang-cao-cht-lng-hiu-qu-ao-to', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"></span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">K hp th hai Quc hi kho XIII:</span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;" id="detail-content">\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong>(GD&T) - Sng nay 2/11, trong phin lm vic ton th ti hi trng, di s iu khin ca Ph Ch tch Quc hi Nguyn Th Kim Ngn, cc i biu Quc hi  dnh thi gian nghe T trnh ca Chnh ph v d n Lut ph bin, gio dc php lut v Bo co thm tra d n Lut ca y ban thng v Quc hi; T trnh ca Chnh ph v d n Lut bo him tin gi v Bo co thm tra d n Lut ca y ban thng v Quc hi; T trnh ca Chnh ph v d n Lut ti nguyn nc (sa i) v Bo co thm tra d n Lut ca y ban thng v Quc hi; T trnh ca Chnh ph v d n Lut gio dc i hc v Bo co thm tra d n Lut ca y ban thng v Quc hi; T trnh ca y ban thng v Quc hi v d kin Chng trnh xy dng lut, php lnh ca Quc hi nhim k kha XIII.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>C th ho cc quy nh v GDH</b></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">D n Lut Gio dc i hc (s gi l D n Lut GDH) l mt trong nhng D n Lut quan trng ca Chnh ph trnh ln Quc hi xin  kin ti K hp ln ny v d kin s tip tc chnh sa, hon thin trn c s tip thu  kin ng gp ca cc i biu Quc hi  trnh Quc hi thng qua ti K hp tip theo.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">T trnh ca Chnh ph v D n Lut do B trng Phm V Lun - tha u quyn ca Th tng Chnh ph - trnh by trong phin lm vic sng nay. y l ln u tin D lut quan trng v GD&T ny c a ra ngh trng Quc hi.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Khng nh v s cn thit ban hnh Lut GDH, T trnh nu r trong bi cnh GDH Vit Nam hi nhp ngy cng su rng vi h thng GDH trong khu vc v trn th gii, vic ban hnh Lut GDH l cn thit  iu chnh cc hot ng GDH ph hp vi cc cam kt quc t, iu c quc t m CHXHCN Vit Nam l thnh vin, qun l tt hn hot ng hp tc, u t nc ngoi trong lnh vc GDH. V vy, vic ban hnh Lut GDH l cn thit, nhm to c s php l vng chc, thng nht cho s pht trin ca GDH v thc hin cc mc tiu ca GDH.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Xt trn gc  quy phm php lut, y l lut chuyn ngnh u tin quy nh v t chc v hot ng GDH, c th ha cc quy nh cn mang tnh khi qut trong Lut GD v GDH.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">C th l: Quy nh v c s GDH (iu 7); Chnh sch ca Nh nc v pht trin GD H (iu 10); Hi ng trng (iu 14), Hi ng qun tr (iu 15), Hiu trng (iu 16); Thnh lp, sp nhp, chia, tch, gii th, cho php, nh ch hot ng o to ca c s GDH (t iu 18 n iu 22); Ch tiu tuyn sinh v t chc tuyn sinh (iu 30); Chng trnh o to, gio trnh GDH (iu 32); Vn bng GDH (iu 34); Hot ng khoa hc v cng ngh (Chng V, t iu 35 n iu 38); Hot ng hp tc quc t (Chng VI, t iu 39 n iu 42); Bo m cht lng v kim nh cht lng GDH (Chng VII, t iu 43 n iu 47).</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">T trnh nu r mt s ni dung quy nh ti Lut GD c sa i, b sung ti d tho Lut GDH ng ch  nh:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Ti iu 41 ca Lut GD quy nh v Chng trnh khung, d tho Lut GDH giao cho B trng B GD&T quy nh v: Chun ti thiu v kin thc, k nng m ngi hc t c sau khi tt nghip; quy trnh xy dng, thm nh v ban hnh chng trnh o to trnh  cao ng, i hc, thc s, tin s; quy nh cc mn hc bt buc trong chng trnh o to i vi cc trnh  o to ca c s gio dc i hc c vn u t nc ngoi; quy nh vic bin son, la chn, thm nh, duyt v s dng ti liu ging dy, gio trnh gio dc i hc (c th hin ti khon 3 iu 32 ca d tho Lut).</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">D tho Lut GDH b sung quy nh v cch xc nh ch tiu tuyn sinh: Ch tiu tuyn sinh c xc nh trn c s nhu cu pht trin kinh t - x hi, ph hp vi cc iu kin v s lng v cht lng i ng ging vin; c s vt cht v thit b (c th hin ti khon 1 iu 30 ca d tho Lut).</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">D tho Lut GDH sa i v b sung quy nh v hi ng trng i vi c s gio dc i hc cng lp so vi quy nh ti iu 52 ca Lut GD (c th hin ti iu 14 d tho Lut) nh sau: Hi ng ai hoc, hi ng trng (gi chung l hi ng trng) c thnh lp  cc c s gio dc i hc cng lp; Ch tch hi ng trng l hiu trng hoc gim c; Th tng Chnh ph quy nh c th v hi ng trng.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Bn cnh , T trnh cng cho bit D Lut b sung quy nh v cch xc nh ch tiu tuyn sinh trn c s cc iu kin m bo cht lng gio dc, bao gm s lng v cht lng i ng ging vin; c s vt cht v thit b. Cc ni dung v c cu t chc, nhim v v quyn hn ca i hc, i hc quc gia; v bo m cht lng v kim nh cht lng gio dc, v li nhun v phi li nhn; v x hi ha v cng bng x hi trong gio dc i hc cng  c  cp trong bn d tho Lut.</span></p>\r\n<table style="float: left; width: 418px; height: 375px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a href="http://gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images591617_image001.jpg"><img src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images591617_image001.jpg" alt="B trng B GD&T Phm V Lun, tha y quyn ca Th tng Chnh ph trnh by T trnh v d n Lut GDH trc Quc hi" height="303" width="400" /></a></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">B trng B GD&T Phm V Lun, tha y quyn ca Th tng Chnh ph trnh by T trnh v d n Lut GDH trc Quc hi</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><b>Hu ht cc vn  ln ca GDH  c  cp</b></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Sau khi nghe B trng B GD&T Phm V Lun, tha y quyn ca Th tng Chnh ph trnh by T trnh v d n Lut GDH, Quc hi  nghe Bo co thm tra d n Lut ca y ban thng v Quc hi, do Ch nhim y ban vn ha, gio dc, thanh nin, thiu nin v nhi ng ca Quc hi o Trng Thi trnh by.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Bo co thm tra cho bit, y ban thng v Quc hi nht tr vi vic cn thit ban hnh Lut GDH  th ch ha cc ch trng, chnh sch ca ng v Nh nc v i mi v pht trin GDH; to hnh lang php l thun li v thng nht  iu chnh ton din cc vn  lin quan n GDH, gp phn i mi cn bn v ton din GDH Vit Nam nhm nng cao cht lng o to, pht trin ngun nhn lc p ng yu cu xy dng v bo v t quc trong thi k i mi v hi nhp quc t.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">V quan im, nguyn tc xy dng Lut, Bo co thm tra cho bit U ban Thng v Quc hi c bn nht tr vi quan im, nguyn tc xy dng Lut GDH trnh by ti T trnh ca Chnh ph v nhn mnh: Th nht, vic xy dng Lut phi bo m th ch ha ng li, quan im ca ng, chnh sch ca Nh nc v pht trin GDH, gp phn gii quyt nhng vn  thc tin va mang tnh cp bch, va mang tnh chin lc;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Th hai, vic xy dng Lut phi hng n mc tiu nng cao cht lng, hiu qu o to; gn o to vi nghin cu khoa hc v chuyn giao cng ngh; bo m cng bng x hi trong GDH; i mi cng tc qun l gio dc, tng cng quyn t ch v trch nhim x hi ca cc c s GDH; Th ba, vi t cch l lut chuyn ngnh, chuyn su cho lnh vc GDH, cc quy nh trong Lut GDH phi c th, chi tit v phi c tnh kh thi cao.\r\n<table style="float: right; width: 275px; height: 122px;" class="quote center" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #993300;"><i>D tho 5 Lut gio dc i hc bao gm 12 chng, 67 iu. Trong qu trnh son tho, Ban son tho  nhn 173  kin ng gp bng vn bn v th in t; hn 220  kin ng gp ti cc hi ngh, hi tho khoa hc ca cc c s gio dc i hc, cc nh khoa hc, cc B, c quan ngang B; y ban Mt trn T quc Vit Nam; y ban Vn ha, Gio dc, Thanh nin, Thiu nin v Nhi ng ca Quc Hi; y ban nhng vn  x hi ca Quc hi; Hip hi cc trng i hc, cao ng ngoi cng lp; Hi Lut gia Vit Nam; Hi khuyn hc; Lin hip cc hi khoa hc k thut Vit Nam; cc c quan bo ch v cc c nhn. </i></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #993300;"><i>Ban son tho Lut gio dc i hc  nghin cu, nghim tc tip thu v hon thin d tho Lut gio dc i hc trc khi trnh ln ngh trng Quc hi ti K hp ln ny  xin  kin ca cc v i biu.</i></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">nh gi chung ca U ban Thng v Quc hi c th hin qua Bo co thm tra cho thy v c bn, vic xy dng D n Lut GDH bo m ng trnh t, th tc, ph hp vi Hin php; ni dung c bn khng mu thun vi h thng php lut hin hnh; hu ht cc vn  ln ca GDH  c  cp trong D tho Lut; mt s quy nh trong cc vn bn di lut v t chc, ti chnh ti sn, o to, nghin cu khoa hc, hp tc quc t, c thc tin kim nghim v c tnh n nh  c php in ha.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Tuy nhin, U ban Thng v Quc hi cng lu  D tho Lut vn cha th ch ha r rng mt s ch trng, chnh sch ln, cha gii quyt thu o, trit  mt s vn  quan trng nh phn tng cc c s GDH, quyn t ch, t chu trch nhim ca c s GDH, c ch, chnh sch i vi cc c s GDH t thc phi li nhun v cc c s GDH t thc v li nhun hp l,; ng thi, cha x l tt mi quan h gia Lut Gio dc hin hnh (lut chung) v Lut GDH (lut chuyn ngnh); mt s iu, khon thay v phi c quy nh c th ngay trong Lut th li c giao cho cc vn bn di lut s gy kh khn v chm tr cho vic trin khai thi hnh Lut trong thc tin.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">V vy, y ban  ngh tip tc nghin cu b sung, hon chnh D n Lut theo hng quy nh c th, chi tit hn na  p ng yu cu ca mt lut chuyn ngnh v gii quyt sm, c hiu qu nhng vn  c bn, cp bch ca GDH hin nay.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Theo d kin chng trnh, ngy 4/11 ti, D n Lut GDH s c cc i biu Quc hi tin hnh tho lun ti t;  n phin lm vic ngy 14/11, Quc hi s a ra tho lun ti Hi trng v nhng vn  cn c  kin khc nhau ca D n Lut GDH.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Bui chiu cng ngy, cc i biu tho lun  t v D kin Chng trnh xy dng lut, php lnh ca Quc hi nhim k kha XIII.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"></span></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 8, '2011-11-15 03:51:40', 62, '', '2011-11-15 08:58:14', 63, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-15 03:51:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 13, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(25, 'Vit Nam c vo top 10 k thi lp trnh vin quc t', 'vit-nam-c-vao-top-10-k-thi-lp-trinh-vien-quc-t', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>(GD&amp;T)- K thi Lp trnh sinh vin quc t ACM/ICPC khu vc Chu  din ra ti Phuket, Thi Lan, Vit Nam  gp mt 2 trong 10 v tr top u ca khu vc. Hai v tr ny thuc v hai i tuyn ca Trng H FPT.</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 500px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images594617_1.jpg"><img alt="2 i tuyn ca H FPT c mt ti Phuket Thi Lan  th hin xut sc trong cuc tranh ti cng 60 i ACM/ICPC" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images594617_1.jpg" height="362" width="500" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">2 i tuyn ca H FPT ti k thi Lp trnh sinh vin quc t ACM/ICPC khu vc Chu </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Kt qu chung cuc, ngi v ch K thi ACM/ICPC khu vc Chu  ti Thi Lan nm nay  thuc v i tuyn Trng H Zhejiang (Trung Quc). Cc i din khc nm trong top 10 cng l cc trng i hc tn tui trn th gii, trong  nhiu trng c xp hng Top 100 trng i hc tt nht th gii nh Trng H Perking (Trung Quc); Trng H Khoa hc cng ngh Hng Kng; Trng H Quc gia Singapore hay cc tn tui ln khc trong khu vc nh Trng H Cng ngh Nanyang (Singapore); Trng H Chulalongkorn (Thi Lan); H Quc gia i Loan<br /> <br /> on Vit Nam c 9 i tuyn tham d n t nhng trng H o to v CNTT xut sc nht trn ton quc nh H Cng ngh - H Quc gia, H Bch khoa TP H Ch Minh, H Khoa hc t nhin, H FPT <br /> <br /> Theo ng L Trng Tng, Hiu trng Trng i hc FPT, k thi ACM/ICPC l mt gii u danh gi ca th gii, l ni m nhng nc mnh nht v CNTT u c i tuyn tham d v cnh tranh quyt lit. Mc tiu tip theo ca H FPT s l tip tc a l c Vit Nam vo vng chung kt ton th gii 2012 ca gii u. <br /> <br /> c bit, ACM/ICPC vng u khu vc tip theo s t chc ti Malaysia vo trung tun thng 11. Vi thnh tch xut sc ln ny, i tuyn trng H FPT s tip tc