(26, 'Nn  sm  trang  b phng php lun trit hc cho HS', 'nen-sm-trang-b-phng-phap-lun-trit-hc-cho-hs', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>(GD&T)-Sinh vin s mn Trit hc dng nh  tr thnh chuyn xa nh tri t. Nhiu ging vin ging dy mn hc ny cng t vn  cp thit cn i mi cch dy v hc Trit hc. Nhng,  ngi hc thc s hiu c s cn thit ca mn hc ny, kh hn na l thc s yu thch mn hc vn l bi ton v cng nan gii.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>\r\n<p><img style="float: right;" alt="alt" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images595317_1.jpg" width="289" height="216" /></p>\r\n</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Sinh vin s Trit</strong></span><br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;">Trong ging ng i hc, mn Trit hc dng nh l mi kinh hong i vi rt nhiu sinh vin, k c nhng sinh vin kh, gii. Khng t sinh vin th nhn mnh kh c th tnh to n cui gi khi hc Trit, cng khng t sinh vin ngm ngi  trt hc bng hoc thm ch l c nm hc v mn hc ny.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Tru tng, kh hiu l cm t thng gp nht khi cc bn sinh vin nhn xt v mn hc ny. Thy Linh  sinh vin Hc vin Bo ch v tuyn truyn tm s khi hc Trit: Thc s, d  rt c gng nhng hu nh em khng hiu c bao nhiu ni dung bi dy trn lp. D thy ging bi rt nhit tnh nhng do ton nhng thut ng chuyn ngnh, qu khi qut, tru tng nn bi hc khng th vo u ni. Sau , em  c gng c sch trc  nh nhng tnh hnh cng khng ci thin c bao nhiu.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Li ging dy cn mang tnh kinh vin, gio iu, bn thn mn hc vi nhng nguyn l, quy lut, phm tr kh hiu khin sinh vin s dn n chn  nh. Nhng, nhiu sinh vin cho rng y l mn hc t ng dng trong thc t khng gip ch g cho cng vic tng lai nn l l, cp tit, ngh hc Chnh v vy, t l sinh vin thi li mn Trit hc lun rt cao.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Ngay c nhng sinh vin theo ngnh Trit hc cng t nhn mnh vt v vi mn hc ny. Nhiu nguyn nhn gp li khin cho ngnh Trit hc ngy cng t c sinh vin la chn. im chun vo ngnh ny thng khng cao nhng cc trng vn phi tuyn n NV2, NV3 mi mong  ch tiu. </span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> <strong>To mi trng trit hc t  lp 1</strong></span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> GS.VS Nguyn Canh Toan cho rng, thc trng dy  hc Trit hc hin nay ging nh vic em hat ging tt gieo ln tha rung cha c chun bi. L mt mn hc kh nhng hoc sinh t ph thng vao ai hoc cha c chun bi mt cach y u, khoa hoc cho vic hoc trit hoc. Ngc lai, cac mn hoc khac it nhiu a co s chun bi t thp ln cao  bc ph thng.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Theo GS.VS Nguyn Canh Toan,  trng ph thng, cho n ht lp 11, cha nn co mn hoc trit hoc nhng nn dung 11 nm t lp 1 n lp 11  tao mi trng v phng phap lun cho hoc sinh. Sau 11 nm tich luy, ln lp 12 cho hoc sinh hoc mt giao trinh trit hoc duy vt bin chng gon, nhe, b ich va khi ln n ai hoc thi sinh vin a co kha nng i su, m rng, ln cao tuy theo nhu cu va hng thu cua tng ngi.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> V vic to mi trng phng php lun cho hc sinh, GS.VS Nguyn Cnh Ton a ra 1 v d sinh ng t vic dy hc ton cho hc sinh lp 1: Lam phep cng 2+9 oi hoi s thng minh la thay 2+9 bng 9+2 (tinh giao hoan cua phep cng): tn dung c s ln la 9, chi cn m thm: 9 cng 1 la 10, 10 cng 1 la 11. Nu la phep cng 8+9 thi cach trn khng co li nhiu vi 8 cung ln nn phai nghi cach khac i 9 thanh 10 - 1 thi se co 8+10 thanh 18, 18 tr 1 thanh 17... Chi cn vi my phep tinh n gian nh trn a co th giao duc c t duy bin chng cho hoc tro, nu giao vin co thm tai nng s pham.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Nhn nh trong bi cnh hin nay, dy Trit th no  chinh phc c ngi hc l mt vn  kh khn, TS Nguyn Th Toan - Khoa Trit hc, Trng i hc S phm H Ni l gii nguyn nhn ch yu do mu thun gia yu cu ca b mn vi trnh  thc t ca i ng ging vin; gia khi lng kin thc  s vi thi gian dy hc b rt ngn; mu thun gia kin thc l lun v thc tin cuc sng; mu thun gia yu cu i mi phng php dy hc theo hng hin i vi iu kin vt cht, trang thit b thiu thn, lc hu v mu thun gia yu cu ca mn hc vi quan nim ca x hi v v tr, vai tr ca mn hc. </span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> TS Nguyn Th Toan cho rng,  Trit hc thc s cn ch ng i vi ngi hc, cn khc phc c nhng im kh trn bng nhng gii php ng b, ton din: s ch o st sao ca cc cp cc ngnh; i mi ni dung chng trnh, gio trnh mt cch khoa hc; u t c s vt cht, trang thit b dy hc hp l; i mi ni dung, phng php, phng tin dy hc theo hng tin tin; thay i  thc, thi  v phng php hc tp; thay i nhn thc x hi v v tr, vai tr mn hc; to lp mi trng kinh t - chnh tr - vn ha lnh mnh thun li cho vic dy Trit hc...</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>(GD&T)</strong></span></p>', '', 1, 4, 0, 11, '2011-11-15 03:55:04', 62, '', '2011-11-23 18:37:12', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-15 03:55:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 7, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor=');
