(27, 'Trn tr dy  hc nhc trong trng ph thng', 'trn-tr-dy--hc-nhc-trong-trng-ph-thong', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>(GD&amp;T)-m nhc tr thnh mn hc chnh thc, c trin khai i tr trn phm vi ton quc dnh cho HS t lp 1 n lp 9 bt u t nm 2002. y l mn hc quan trng trong qu trnh gip cc em HS pht trin ton din. Tuy nhin, hin, vic qu thiu nhng bi ht hay dnh cho la tui hc tr cng vi mt s hn ch trong chng trnh o to gio vin m nhc khin hu ht nhng ngi trong cuc bn khon, trn tr.</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 425px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201110/original/images588823_1.JPG" alt="Bc Ninh a ht quan h vo trng hc" height="317" width="425" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">Bc Ninh a ht quan h vo trng hc</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ca khc hay cho la tui hc tr: thiu trm trng</strong><br /> <br /> C gio o Khnh Ly - Trng THCS Vit Nam- Angiri trn tr, trc y Hi Nhc s Vit Nam  thnh lp mt ban sng tc cho thiu nhi v t chc mt s hi tho chuyn  v thiu nhi, nhng t nm 1989 n nay th t chc ny khng cn na, sng tc cho thiu nhi c phn v cc ban thanh nhc, chi hi nhc s ti cc tnh. S lng nhc s tr hin nay l rt ng nhng v sao li  thiu ht trm trng ca khc thiu nhi? Phi chng sng tc nhc cho thiu nhi l qu kh? Thc trng v ca khc vit cho thiu nhi c th ni rng rt thiu, rt yu. Nhu cu th cao m khng c p li nn cc em quay sang nghe, ht nhc ngi ln, c bit l nhc nc ngoi, nhc tr, nhc Hn Quc, nhc Trung Quc, nhc Nht Bn, nhc Anh, nhc M... iu ny khin cc em khng th thot khi gng p trong suy ngh, tm t, tnh cm v gi i rt nhiu so vi  tui.<br /> <br /> ThS. Nguyn Th Hi - Khoa S phm m nhc-M Thut (H S phm H Ni) th khng nh, nhu cu v m nhc cho cc la tui trong cc trng hc rt ln. C nc c ti trn di 15 nghn trng Tiu hc, gn 10 nghn trng THCS, hng nghn trng THPT v c chc nghn trng mm non (mu gio) vi tng s hc sinh trn di 20 triu em. Hot ng Gio dc m nhc  c mt  khp cc cp hc t mm non n THPT m trong  ca ht l mt ni dung gi vai tr quan trng nht. Thc t hin ti, lng bi ht cho la tui mm non nhiu hn cho la tui HS Tiu hc. Lng bi bt vit cho tui HS THCS c t l rt cao so vi s bi ht vit cho i tng HS THPT. V th, 2 i tng HS Tiu hc v THPT cn c quan tm vit cho cc em nhiu hn na.<br /> <br /> ThS. Nguyn Th Hi cng cho rng, vi s lng bi ht c a vo sch m nhc Tiu hc v THCS tng cng khong trn di 100 bi (bao gm c dn ca v mt s ca khc nc ngoi), chng trnh  c thc hin gn 10 nm nay, cng  bc l nhng u im v nhc im kh r. Bn cnh a s bi c cc em tip nhn th c bi cn cha ph hp vi  tui v qu di, c bi li qu ngn khi a vo tng lp hoc s dng  mt cp hc c th, d ni dung v ngh thut ca tc phm kh tt.<br /> <br /> Theo ThS. NS. L Anh Tun - Vin Khoa hc Gio dc Vit Nam, ni n ca khc trong nh trng ph thng hin nay, cn quan tm n mt s vn  nh,  nh trng, HS c hc nhng loi ca khc nh th no? S lng ca khc cho HS hin  y  cha, thiu hay tha? Cht lng ca khc trong chng trnh gio dc mn m nhc hin nay th no? La chn ca khc cho HS  tng lp  ph hp cha? HS gp nhng thun li g, kh khn g khi hc ca khc? HS c yu thch cc ca khc c hc hay khng?<br /> <br /> Trong chng trnh mn m nhc, bi ht thng c dy trong mt tit (Tiu hc l 35 pht, THCS l 45 pht), sau  cn c n tp trong mt vi tit hc tip theo. Hin nay, vi 83 bi ht m HS c hc t lp 1 n lp 9, s lng nh vy l ph hp, cng thm hng chc bi ht, bn nhc m HS c nghe khi c hc thng qua cc ni dung khc th vn hiu bit v ca khc ca cc em l kh ln. Tuy nhin,  trng THPT hin khng dy m nhc, nn nhng ca khc dnh cho la tui ny hon ton b nn m nhc th trng thao tng, nh trng khng kim sot c v s lng v cht lng ca chng, nhng hu qu do HS THPT khng c hng s gio dc m nhc c th s l vn  cn nhiu s trao i.<br /> <br /> V cht lng ca khc trong chng trnh gio dc mn m nhc hin nay.,  la chn 1 bi ht a vo chng trnh gio dc mn m nhc, nhng tiu ch c quan tm hng u bao gi cng l: bi ht hay, c gi tr ngh thut, m bo tnh ph thng, s chun mc, tnh ph hp v va sc Tuy nhin, nh gi v ci hay, ci p trong ngh thut, phn ln ch da vo cm nhn ca ring mnh. Khi bin son SGK m nhc, vic la chn v  xut bi ht a vo chng trnh cng da vo cm nhn ca tng c nhn v c nhm tc gi, vic la chn  i khi vn phin din v c th ni, khng bao gi lm hi lng tt c mi ngi. Bi v mt bi ht, mt tc phm cho d hay n my, vn s c nhng ngi khng yu thch v khng quan tm n n.<br /> <br /> <strong>Chng trnh o to GV m nhc thiu tnh ng b, tnh thng nht </strong><br /> <br /> Theo ThS. o ng Phng, Trng phng o to HSP ngh thut TW, t nm 2001 n nay, B GD&amp;T  k v cho ban hnh 231 chng trnh khung gio dc i hc, trong  c 176 chng trnh khung trnh  i hc, 53 chng trnh khung trnh  cao ng v 01 chng trnh khung Gio dc ho nhp. Trong tng s 176 Chng trnh khung trnh  i hc ch c 20 l ca khi ngnh Vn ho - Ngh thut; v trong s 53 Chng trnh khung trnh  cao ng, khng c mt chng trnh no v khi ngnh Vn ho - Ngh thut.<br /> <br /> Bn cnh vic xy dng chng trnh khung ca B GD&amp;T, B Vn ho - Th thao v Du lch cng  r sot, xy dng v ban hnh mt lot chng trnh khung  trnh  trung cp v khi cc ngnh Vn ho - Ngh thut cho cc trng Vn ho - Ngh thut trn ton quc.<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /> Tuy nhin, trong tng s cc chng trnh khung c ban hnh t trnh  trung cp n trnh  i hc ni chung, c bit l chng trnh o to khi ngnh Vn ho - Ngh thut ni ring, th cha c mt chng trnh khung no v o to gio vin m nhc, M thut do B GD&amp;T hay B Vn ho - Th thao v Du lch ban hnh, m hu ht do cc trng t xy dng, trnh B Gio dc &amp; o to hoc B Vn ho - Th thao v Du lch duyt, sau  tin hnh thc hin. iu  cho thy chng trnh o to gio vin m nhc, M thut thiu tnh ng b, tnh thng nht v bc l mt s hn ch.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> Mt s chng trnh  tr nn bt cp, c, khng cp nht c tri thc khoa hc - cng ngh mi, tin tin. Khi lng kin thc bt buc ca chng trnh cn qu cao  70 n 80%&nbsp; so vi tng khi lng o to ton kho,  lm gim i tnh linh hot ca cc chng trnh khung cng nh s ch ng ca cc nh trng trong pht trin chng trnh o to. Chng trnh cn hn ch v s lng v cht lng, cha ph hp vi s pht trin ca khoa hc v cng ngh, tnh thc tin v khoa hc khng cao, nht l khng m bo s lin thng dc (gia cc trnh  o to) v s lin thng ngang (gia cc ngnh cng trnh )...</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> nhiu chng trnh o to, ni dung kin thc ngnh chnh khng  khi lng kin thc ct li ti thiu; b tr mn hc vo cc khi kin thc khng hp l, c nhng mn thuc kin thc i cng li c a vo khi kin thc chuyn ngnh hoc ngc li. Mt s mn hc ni dung khng tng thch, khng ph hp vi trnh  o to. <br /> <br /> ThS. o ng Phng cho rng, khi thit k, xy dng mt chng trnh o to, trc ht cn phi tr li 2 cu hi: Sinh vin s t c nhng kin thc, k nng, thi  ton din no sau khi tt nghip ra trng ? Lm th no  chng ta c th lm tt hn trong vic m bo sinh vin t c nhng kin thc, k nng y ?<br /> <br />  tr li c cho 2 cu hi trn, theo ThS. o ng Phng cn thit phi xy dng pht trin chng trnh o to theo hng tip cn CDIO. Theo , cc ni dung chnh p dng ca cch tip cn CDIO  pht trin chng trnh o to gio vin s phm m nhc, M thut gm xy dng h thng mc tiu o to (chun u ra) chung cho gio vin; cc ngnh s dng h mc tiu ny  xy dng chng trnh o to cho cc ngnh ca mnh; xy dng v trin khai cc phng php chuyn ti chng trnh mi son; xy dng v trin khai phng php kim tra, nh gi kt qu hc tp theo chng trnh mi son c. ng thi, xy dng b tiu chun mi v trin khai kim nh hot ng o to theo chng trnh mi.</p>', '', 1, 7, 0, 39, '2011-11-15 03:56:03', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-15 03:56:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 21, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(28, 'Tuyn sinh H-C 2012 s c 1 s iu chnh, b sung', 'tuyn-sinh-h-c-2012-s-co-1-s-iu-chnh-b-sung', '', '<p></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>(GD&T)-B GD&T cho bit, k thi tuyn sinh H, C h chnh quy 2012 v c bn v gi n nh theo gii php 3 chung, nhng s c nhng iu chnh, b sung mt cch hp l theo hng m rng khi thi, iu chnh phng thc tuyn sinh i vi cc ngnh nng khiu, b sung chnh sch i vi hc sinh gii quc gia...</strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 480px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="alt" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201110/original/images590377_1.jpg" height="377" width="480" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , s tip tc gim ch tiu khng chnh quy, gim dn ch tiu tuyn sinh TCCN trong cc trng H, C, ng thi tng cng cc iu kin bo m cht lng  tng bc nng cao cht lng o to chnh quy.<br /> <br /> Cng vi , t chc qun l cht ch qu trnh o to, c bit tng cng cng tc qun l ging dy, qun l hc tp, sit cht quy ch thi, kim tra v nh gi; xy dng ngn hng cu hi thi  tch khu dy v khu thi.<br /> <br /> Ti hi ngh trc tuyn s kt 1,5 nm thc hin Ch th s 296/CT-TTG ca Th tng Chnh ph v tng kt nm hc 2010 - 2011 khi cc trng H, C, B trng B GD&T Phm V Lun cho bit, mt s ngnh, trng khng tuyn  ch tiu, trong  c nhng ngnh quan trng nh khoa hc c bn, nng lm nghip, hn nm, s phm... mc d  c nhiu gii php u i nhng vn khng thu ht c sinh vin. B trng khng nh, B GD&T v cc b ngnh s bn bc, tham kho  kin  c nhng bin php v m; nhng mt s trng, ngnh khng ht c th sinh, theo B trng cn c nguyn nhn trc tip l do iu kin m bo cht lng rt km. <br /> <br /> c bit, k thi tuyn sinh 2011 c 217 lt trng H v 130 trng C c t chc thi; 146 trng H, C khng t chc thi m da vo kt qu thi theo  thi chung  xt tuyn. K thi c 2.183.630 h s KDT, s th sinh d thi l 1.696.250 (t 77.68%) cao hn nm 2010 xp x 1,5%</p>', '', 1, 8, 0, 3, '2011-11-15 03:58:38', 62, '', '2011-11-17 05:59:11', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-15 03:58:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 25, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(29, 'Tuyn n vi cc trng CAND t 10-15%', 'tuyn-n-vi-cac-trng-cand-t-10-15', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>(GD&amp;TD)-B Cng an va ban hnh Thng t 71/2011/TT-BCA quy nh tuyn sinh vo cc trng Cng an nhn dn (bao gm cc hc vin, trng i hc, cao ng, trung cp, vn ha Cng an nhn dn). Thng t ny thay th Quyt nh s 727/2006/Q-BCA.<br /> </strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 300px;" class="image rightside" align="right" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="Sinh vin Hc vin Cnh st trong gi hc bn (nh MH)" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201110/original/images590137_images.jpg" height="219" width="300" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center"><span style="font-size: x-small;">Sinh vin Hc vin Cnh st nhn dn trong gi hc bn (nh MH)</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vic tuyn sinh i vi n hc sinh vo cc trng Cng an nhn dn c xc nh ch tiu ring vi t l t 10-15% trn tng ch tiu o to ca tng ngnh hc v tng trng.<br /> <br /> Theo , tuyn sinh vo cc trng Cng an nhn dn c thc hin trn c s kt hp gia kim tra hc lc, sc khe, nng khiu, tiu chun chnh tr, phm cht o c ca ngi d tuyn theo quy nh ring ca B Cng an vi kt qu thi tuyn, c tuyn, xt tuyn theo quy ch tuyn sinh ca B Gio dc v o to v quy nh ca B Cng an.<br /> <br /> i vi tuyn sinh o to tin s, Thng t nu r, iu kin ng k d tuyn, ngoi nhng quy nh v iu kin ng k d tuyn theo quy ch o to trnh  tin s hin hnh ca B Gio dc v o to..., tui ca ngi d tuyn l khng qu 50; i vi tuyn sinh o to thc s,  tui ca ngi d tuyn khng qu 45 tui.<br /> <br /> Quy nh v tuyn sinh i hc, cao ng h chnh quy, Thng t nu r, v  tui, i vi cn b, chin s cng an trong bin ch khng qu 30 tui, i vi hc sinh, khng qu 20 tui, ring hc sinh l ngi dn tc thiu s khng qu 22 tui th mi  iu kin ng k d thi.V tiu chun sc khe, nam phi t chiu cao t 1,64m n 1,80m v cn nng t 48 kg n 75 kg; n phi c chiu cao t 1,58m n 1,75m v cn nng t 45 kg n 60 kg.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong mt nm, mi th sinh ch c ng k d thi vo 1 ngnh hc  mt trng. Vic t chc thi tuyn ca tng ngnh hc  tng trng c thc hin theo hng dn tuyn sinh hng nm ca B Cng an.</p>', '', 1, 8, 0, 3, '2011-11-15 04:00:14', 62, '', '2011-11-23 09:21:56', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-15 04:00:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 17, 'robots=\nauthor='),
