(31, 'Cng b 17 sn phm CNTT vo chung kho Nhn ti t Vit 2011', 'cong-b-17-sn-phm-cntt-vao-chung-kho-nhan-tai-t-vit-2011', '', '<div id="detail-content">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 8pt;">(GD&T)  Hm nay (1/11), Ban t chc Gii thng Nhn ti t Vit 2011  cng b kt qu vng s kho gii thng trong lnh vc cng ngh thng tin nm nay.</span> </strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 400px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="cvcvcvc" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images591117_1.JPG" height="280" width="400" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Gii thng Nhn ti t Vit nm th 7 trong lnh vc CNTT c tng 204 sn phm tham d. Trong  c 154 sn phm phn mm, 16 sn phm phn cng, gii php mng v tch hp cng ngh: 34 sn phm; sn phm  ng dng: 65 sn phm, sn phm c tim nng ng dng: 139 sn phm.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong lnh vc CNTT, th sinh nh tui nht l em Hong Thn, sinh nm 2000, n t H Ni. Th sinh ln tui nht l inh Cng Ninh, sinh nm 1967, n t Thnh ph H Ch Minh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Qua vic phn tch, tm hiu v nh gi v hiu qu ca cc sn phm tham d, Hi ng S kho Gii thng Nhn ti t Vit 2011 trong lnh vc CNTT  chnh thc chn ra 17 sn phm tt nht  tranh ti ti vng chung kho.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">D kin trong hai ngy 17 v 18/11 ti, cc th sinh tham d ni dung CNTT c lt vo vng chung kho s tp trung ti H Ni  thuyt trnh v bo v sn phm trc Hi ng Chung kho.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">V lnh vc Khoa hc t nhin v Y dc, cc cng trnh nghin cu ang c Hi ng Khoa hc thuc Vin Khoa hc & Cng ngh Vit Nam v Hi ng khoa hc- B Y t tip tc xem xt  thng bo chnh thc ti Ban t chc Gii thng danh sch cc nh khoa hc c tn vinh vo L trao gii ngy 20/11/2011.</p>\r\n<p>Danh sch cc sn phm lt vo vng Chung kho Gii thng Nhn ti t Vit 2011:</p>\r\n<p><b>Cc sn phm  ng dng rng ri </b></p>\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr