(33, 'Ton vn pht biu ca Tng B th, Ch tch Quc hi Nguyn Ph Trng', 'toan-vn-phat-biu-ca-tng-bi-th-ch-tch-quc-hi-nguyn-phu-trng', '', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2">Trn trng gii thiu vi bn c ton vn bi pht biu ca Tng B th, Ch tch Quc hi Nguyn Ph Trng ti L K nim 80 nm ngy thnh lp on TNCS H Ch Minh (26/3/1931 - 26/3/2011) v n nhn Hun chng Sao vng ln II.</span></p>\r\n<div class="body_description">\r\n<div align="justify"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"></span></strong>\r\n<div align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2">-----------------</span></div>\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;" face="Arial" size="2">\r\n<p style="text-align: right;" align="right">H Ni, ngy 25 thng 3 nm 2011</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Knh tha ng ch Nguyn Ph Trng, Tng B th BCH Trung ng ng Cng sn Vit Nam.<br />Knh tha cc ng ch lnh o, nguyn lnh o ng, Nh nc, Mt trn T quc Vit Nam.<br />Knh tha cc ng ch lnh o on TNCS H Ch Minh cc thi k.<br />Knh tha cc ng ch i biu.<br />Tha cc v khch quc t.<br />Cc ng ch on vin v thanh nin thn mn.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Hm nay, on Thanh nin cng sn H Ch Minh long trng k nim 80 nm ngy thnh lp v n nhn Hun chng Sao vng ln 2. Thay mt Ban Chp hnh Trung ng on, ti nhit lit cho mng v knh chc sc khe cc ng ch lnh o, nguyn lnh o ng, Nh nc, Mt trn T quc Vit Nam, lnh o cc ban, b, ngnh, on th Trung ng v a phng, cc ng ch lo thnh cch mng, M Vit Nam anh hng, lnh o on TNCS H Ch Minh cc thi k; cc v i biu khch qu; xin gi n ton th cn b, on vin, thanh thiu nhi c nc v on vin, thanh nin ang hc tp, cng tc  nc ngoi li chc mng tt p nht.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Trong gi pht trng th ny, chng ta thnh knh tng nh v bit n v hn Bc H knh yu - Ngi  cng ng sng lp v rn luyn on TNCS H Ch Minh,  ch ra cho thanh nin l tng sng v con ng ng n  thc hin l tng, Ngi   li mun vn tnh thng yu cho thanh nin, thiu nin v nhi ng. Chng ta tng nh v bit n cc th h cha anh  hy sinh cho s nghip cch mng ca ng, ca dn tc,  tui tr hm nay c sng trong ho bnh, hnh phc, c hc hnh v pht trin.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tha cc ng ch v cc bn,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Ngay t khi va ra i, trong khng kh sc si cch mng ca phong tro X Vit Ngh Tnh, ch vi nhng on vin u tin, on TNCS ng Dng, nay l on TNCS H Ch Minh  tch cc gic ng cho thanh nin l tng ca ng, vn ng thanh nin theo ng lm cch mng. Th h nhng on vin u tin, kin trung bt khut m in hnh l L T Trng vi cu ni bt h con ng ca thanh nin ch c th l con ng cch mng  thi thc cc th h thanh nin tip ni i theo con ng cch mng ca ng v Bc H, cng vi cc tng lp nhn dn lm nn nhng chin tch thn k trong u tranh ginh c lp, xy dng v bo v t quc. </span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> l th h thanh nin</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> khao kht t do, c thc tnh bi l tng ca ng, di s t chc ca on Thanh nin cu quc  cng hn 30 triu ng bo c nc thc hin li ku gi ca Ch tch H Ch Minh D c phi t chy dy Trng Sn cng phi dnh cho c c lp, t do, r bn ng dy sng la lm nn Cch mng thng Tm lch s; Ngay trong nhng ngy u lm ngi dn t do ca mt t nc t do v c lp, thanh nin  xung phong chng gic i, dit gic dt, u tranh chnh tr chng th trong, gic ngoi, bo v chnh quyn cch mng non tr. </span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> l th h thanh nin</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> Quyt t cho t quc quyt sinh, "ng ln p li sng ni", xp bt nghin ln ng tranh u mt lng theo ng, theo Bc H thc hin cuc khng chin gian kh, trng k, lm nn chin thng in Bin lng ly nm chu, chn ng a cu! Th h thanh nin y  gp phn lm rng r dn tc, v vang ging ni, vi nhng tm gng tui tr sng ngi nh La Vn Cu, C Chnh Lan, V Th Su, Trn Vn n, B Vn n, T Vnh Din ; </span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> l th h thanh nin Ba sn sng  chch mu mnh vit th tnh nguyn ln ng git gic bng quyt tm X dc Trng Sn i cu nc  min Bc, Nm xung phong  min Nam. Cc Anh, cc Ch  chin u hy sinh v cng oanh lit trn mi no ng ca t nc, khi i din vi qun th cng nh ngay trong lng ch, t Hm Rng, Nam Ngn; Thnh C Qung Tr, ng 9 - Khe Sanh, Trung Bn, ng Lcn in Bn, Tc Dp, Vng R, Bu Bng, p Bc, t thp C Chi, Si Gn  Gia nh lp nn nhng k tch v vang, cng vi ton qun, ton dn ta dnh thng li v i, gii phng min Nam, thu non sng v mt mi. Th h anh hng, thng M v vang  tc vo lch s on nhng tm gng sng ngi ca ch ngha anh hng cch mng nh Nguyn Vn Tri, Nguyn Vit Xun, L Th Hng Gm, Nguyn Vit Hng, Kp Klng, Nguyn Vn Thc, ng Thy Trm, 10 c gi thanh nin xung phong ng Lc </span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> l th h thanh nin</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> trong nim vui trng phng ca ngy i thng, bt tay vo hn gn vt thng chin tranh, hng hi tham gia cc phong tro lao ng, sn xut, r ph bom mn, phc ha, khai hoang, xy dng nhng khu kinh t mi, lm ng giao thng, cng trnh thy in, xy dng cc nh my, nng trng, gi vng bin cng v lm ngha v quc t H sn sng i ti nhng ni gian kh, khng ngi vt qua bo ging, nng la.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> l th h thanh nin </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">kin nh dng cao ngn c c lp dn tc v ch ngha x hi trong bi cnh bin ng  Lin X v ng u, i u trong i mi, bng nim tin, tr tu, sc tr, quyt tm lp nghip v gi nc, thi ua tnh nguyn vt qua khng hong kinh t - x hi vi nhng cng trnh thanh nin cng sn khai ph t hoang, xy o thanh nin, dng lng lp nghip ti vng bin gii, hi o; gp phn cng vi ton ng, ton dn, ton qun lp nn nhng thnh tu to ln, c  ngha lch s ca 20 nm i mi.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Knh tha cc ng ch,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T sau i hi on ton quc ln th IX, hai phong tro 5 xung kch pht trin kinh t - x hi; bo v T quc, 4 ng hnh vi thanh nin lp thn, lp nghip i vo cuc sng, va pht huy vai tr xung kch, tnh nguyn ca tui tr trong pht trin kinh t- x hi, gi vng quc phng an ninh, m bo an sinh x hi; ng thi h tr gii quyt cc nhu cu, nguyn vng chnh ng ca thanh nin; Cc phong tro thanh nin tnh nguyn, Khi T quc cn, V bin cng t quc, Bo v mi trng v ng ph vi bin i kh hu, khc phc hu qu bo l, Bo v dng sng qu hng, gi gn trt t an ton v xy dng vn ho giao thng, xy nh bn tr dn nui, hin mu cu ngi, h tr tr em c hon cnh kh khn c gii tr hng ng, c d lun x hi ng tnh, tin cy;  v ang khc ha hnh nh th h thanh nin thi k mi, lun trung thnh tuyt i v tin tng vo s lnh o ca ng, nu cao lng yu nc v trch nhim cng dn, dm dn thn, tnh nguyn v cng ng, n nhng ni gian kh, m nhn nhng vic mi, vic kh vi  ch quyt tm a t nc vn ln.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T chc on khng ngng c cng c v ln mnh, t 8 on vin u tin do Bc H trc tip rn luyn, on TNCS H Ch Minh  pht trin mnh  63 tnh, thnh v 5 khi trc thuc, vi hn 32 nghn c s, hn 6,5 triu on vin. Trong 10 nm, t nm 2001 n nm 2010,  gii thiu cho ng 2.342.897 on vin u t v c ng xem xt kt np 1.065.895 ng ch, chim hn 65% tng s ng vin mi kt np. Mt trn on kt tp hp thanh nin khng ngng m rng vi s pht trin mnh m ca Hi Lin hip thanh nin v cc t chc thnh vin tp th.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Quan h hp tc gia on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh vi t chc thanh nin cc nc v cc t chc quc t c cng c v m rng, tng cng quan h hu ngh v hiu bit ln nhau gia thanh nin Vit Nam vi thanh nin v nhn dn cc nc; to iu kin nng cao nhn thc v hi nhp quc t cho on vin thanh nin; gp phn tch cc vo thnh cng ca cng tc i ngoi nhn dn; nng cao uy tn v v th ca thanh nin Vit Nam trn trng quc t.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">80 nm ln mnh v trng thnh trong s nghip cch mng ca ng, ca dn tc  hun c nn truyn thng v vang ca on TNCS H Ch Minh v tui tr Vit Nam, ng thi cng rt ra nhng bi hc kinh nghim qu bu  tip tc xy dng on TNCS H Ch Minh thc s vng mnh, xng ng l trng hc x hi ch ngha ca tui tr, l i d b tin cy ca ng Cng sn Vit Nam.  l bi hc v nu cao lng yu nc, lun trung thnh v tin tng tuyt i vo s lnh o ca ng, vo tnh hin thc v thng li ca l tng x hi ch ngha; bit k tha v pht huy truyn thng v vang ca cc th h cha anh, khng ngng i mi  xy dng on vng mnh v chnh tr, t chc v hnh ng; xc nh ni dung phong tro hnh ng cch mng bm st i hi ca thc tin cuc sng, p ng ng yu cu nhim v cch mng, ph hp vi li ch chnh ng, hp php v khao kht cao p ca thanh nin; quan tm chm lo, bo v quyn v li ch chnh ng ca thanh thiu nhi; kin tr tham mu xy dng chnh sch pht trin thanh nin; xy dng i ng cn b c o c v nng lc thc tin, am hiu v gn b vi thanh nin, c kh nng i thoi v nh hng cho thanh nin, nng ng, sng to, dm dn thn, sn sng m nhn vic mi, i n nhng ni gian kh.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Knh tha cc ng ch v cc bn,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Trong nim hn hoan ca ngy hi ln, vinh d trc phn thng cao qu  Hun chng Sao vng ln 2, chng ta li suy ngh v trch nhim ca on v tui tr trong chng ng nc rt a nc ta thnh mt nc cng nghip theo hng hin i vo nm 2020. on TNCS H Ch Minh v tui tr c nc vui mng khi Ngh quyt i hi i biu ton quc ln th XI ca ng khng nh: Lm tt cng tc gio dc chnh tr, t tng, truyn thng, l tng, o c v li sng, to iu kin hc tp, lao ng, gii tr, pht trin th lc, tr tu cho th h tr; khuyn khch, c v thanh nin nui dng c m, hoi bo ln, xung kch, sng to, lm ch khoa hc, cng ngh hin i; hnh thnh mt lp thanh nin u t trn mi lnh vc, k tc trung thnh v xut sc s nghip cch mng ca ng, ca dn tc. Nim tin v s k vng  l ng lc to ln  on TNCS H Ch Minh khng ngng i mi ni dung v phng thc hot ng, lm tt cc nhim v sau y:</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Mt l,</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> i mi cng tc gio dc chnh tr, t tng, truyn thng, l tng, o c v li sng cho ph hp vi c im ca tng i tng thanh nin. Thc hin tht tt cuc vn ng Tui tr Vit Nam hc tp v lm theo li Bc v chng trnh Thp sng c m tui tr Vit Nam v dn giu, nc mnh, dn ch, cng bng, vn minh; xy dng v nhn rng c nhiu c nhn, tp th thanh nin tin tin, hnh thnh lp thanh nin u t l nhng ngi c lng yu nc, c o c  lm gng, c tr tu  nhn bit, c  ch  vn ln, c bn lnh  hi nhp, c quyt tm  hnh ng; truyn i cm hng phn u khng ngng, lun vn ln khng nh mnh, khng ngng sng to cng to dng tng lai, thc hin thng li mc tiu l tng x hi ch ngha.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Hai l,</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> t chc hiu qu phong tro Bn ng hnh vi thanh nin lp thn, lp nghip, h tr thanh nin nng cao trnh  hc vn, chuyn mn, ngh nghip; pht trin k nng x hi, nng cao nng lc hi nhp; nng lc sng to, kh nng ng dng thnh tu khoa hc, cng ngh; gp phn hnh thnh ngun nhn lc cht lng cao phc v s nghip y mnh cng nghip ho, hin i ho; n lc vun trng  hnh thnh nhng cn b qun l tr gii, nh khoa hc tr gii, doanh nhn tr gii, ngi cng nhn tr gii, nng dn tr gii, s quan tr gii. ng vai tr u tu  thc y ng o thanh nin hnh ng c hiu qu, thc hin thng li chin lc pht trin kinh t x hi 2011-2020. </span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Ba l,</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> pht trin phong tro Nm xung kch pht trin kinh t - x hi v bo v T quc  pht huy mnh m vai tr xung kch ca thanh nin trong lao ng sng to, sn xut kinh doanh, ci cch hnh chnh, gi vng quc phng an ninh, trt t an ton x hi, m bo an sinh x hi; t chc thc hin hiu qu cc cng trnh, phn vic thanh nin. Tham mu cho Nh nc ban hnh cc chnh sch  pht trin thanh nin, thu ht thanh nin tham gia pht trin kinh t x hi  vng su, vng xa, vng c bit kh khn; chnh sch ti nng tr, chnh sch cho thanh nin tnh nguyn trong iu kin mi. </span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Bn l,</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> qun trit quan im xy dng on l gp phn xy dng ng trc mt bc, khng ngng xy dng, cng c t chc on TNCS H Ch Minh vng mnh v chnh tr, t tng, t chc v hnh ng, xng ng l i d b tin cy ca ng, thc s l trng hc x hi ch ngha ca thanh nin. c bit coi trng nng cao cht lng t chc c s on v cht lng i ng cn b, thng xuyn gii thiu cho ng nhng on vin u t c cht lng, nhng cn b on tm huyt, c o c v gn b vi qun chng, c tr tu v nng lc t chc hot ng thc tin, dm ngh, dm lm, dm chu trch nhim, dm dn thn vo nhng kh khn  b sung ngun sinh lc mi cho ng p ng yu cu xy dng ng, tip tc nng cao nng lc lnh o v sc chin u ca ng trong thi k y mnh cng nghip ha, hin i ha t nc.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Nm l, </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">tip tc tng cng cng tc on kt, tp hp thanh nin theo phng chm on phi mnh, Hi phi rng; va m bo vai tr nng ct chnh tr ca on TNCS H Ch Minh, va pht huy tnh ch ng ca Hi Lin hip Thanh nin v cc t chc thnh vin tp th ca Hi   u c thanh nin,   c t chc Hi; pht trin mnh cc t chc thnh vin tp th ca Hi Lin hip thanh nin theo ngnh ngh, s thch; tng cng cng tc on kt tp hp thanh nin dn tc, tn gio v thanh nin, sinh vin Vit Nam  nc ngoi.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Knh tha cc ng ch,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T ho v truyn thng lch s v vang ca on TNCS H Ch Minh trong 80 nm qua, bng sc tr v nhit huyt ca tui thanh xun, bng nim tin khng lay chuyn v lng trung thnh tuyt i vi ng, vi dn tc, th h cn b, on vin, thanh nin hm nay s vit tip truyn thng v vang ca on TNCS H Ch Minh v thanh nin Vit Nam bng s n lc phn u hon thnh xut sc nhim v ca mnh trong cng nghip ha, hin i ha, hi nhp quc t, xy dng v bo v t quc Vit Nam x hi ch ngha, v dn giu, nc mnh, dn ch, cng bng, vn minh.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Ban B th Trung ng on ku gi Ban chp hnh on mi cp u c cng trnh, phn vic thanh nin; mi on vin u c vic lm thit thc tham gia gii quyt cc vn  bc xc  ngay a phng, n v ca mnh, thc hin thng li nhim v Nm Thanh nin 2011, a Ngh quyt i hi XI ca ng vo cuc sng, lm nn nhng o hoa ti thm dng ln ng v Bc H knh yu. y chnh l cch tt nht, c th nht, su sc nht  on TNCS H Ch Minh v tui tr Vit Nam by t long bit n su sc i vi s chm lo n cn ca ng v chnh quyn cc cp; s to iu kin v hp tc c hiu qu ca cc b, ngnh, on th, cc t chc x hi, cc t chc kinh t, cc nhn s, tr thc, cc nh khoa hc, cc vn ngh s, cc bc ph huynh, cc cn b on qua cc thi k. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Mt ln na, xin gi ti cc ng ch lnh o ng, Nh nc, Mt trn T quc Vit Nam, cc v i biu khch qu cng ton th cc ng ch v cc bn li chc tt p nht.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Trn trng cm n./.</span></p>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>', 1, 6, 0, 24, '2011-11-15 04:12:15', 62, '', '2011-11-17 08:24:48', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-11-15 04:12:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 29, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(34, '"ng, Nh nc v nhn dn lun nh gi cao cng lao to ln ca thanh nin Vit Nam qua cc thi k cch mng v dnh s quan tm c bit i vi th h tr"...', 'qeng-nha-nc-va-nhan-dan-luon-anh-gia-cao-cong-lao-to-ln-ca-thanh-nien-vit-nam-qua-cac-thi-k-cach-mng-va-danh-s-quan-tam-c-bit-i-vi-th-h-trq', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" face="Arial" size="2"></span><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;" face="Arial" size="2"><span face="Arial" size="2"> "ng, Nh nc v nhn dn lun nh gi cao cng lao to ln ca thanh nin Vit Nam qua cc thi k cch mng v dnh s quan tm c bit i vi th h tr"...  l li ch o ca Tng B th, Ch tch Quc hi Nguyn Ph Trng ti L k nim 80 nm thnh lp on TNCS H CH Minh (26/3/1931-26/3/2011) v n nhn Hun chng Sao vng (ln 2). </span></span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial;" face="Arial" size="2"><strong>Ban bin tp Cng Thng tin in t Trung ng on trn trng gii thiu ton vn bi pht biu quan trng ny.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<div align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" face="Arial" size="2"><img title="Tng B th, Ch tch Quc hi Nguyn Ph Trng, pht biu ti L k nim" style="width: 400px; height: 281px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://doanthanhnien.vn/admin/Upload/NewsFolder/2011/3/12/483TBT1a.jpg" height="281px" width="400px" /><em><strong><span style="color: #0000ff; font-family: Arial;" face="Arial" size="2" color="#0000ff"></span></strong></em></span></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tha cc v khch qu,</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tha cc ng ch,</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Nhn dp k nim 80 nm Ngy thnh lp on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh v n nhn Hun chng Sao Vng ln th hai - phn thng cao qu ca ng v Nh nc trao tng th h tr, ti thn i gi n cc v i biu, cc v khch qu, cc ng ch cn b on qua cc thi k, v qua cc ng ch gi ti ton th cn b, on vin, hi vin, thanh nin, thiu nin v nhi ng c nc li thm hi chn tnh v li chc mng tt p nht.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tha cc ng ch v cc bn,</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Trong sut chiu di lch s, tui tr nc ta ht th h ny n th h khc,  nu cao truyn thng yu nc, ch kh anh hng, cng hin to ln vo s nghip dng nc v gi nc.</span></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Trong thi i H Ch Minh, vi s ra i ca on Thanh nin Cng sn ng Dng (nay l on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh) do ng v Bc H sng lp, lnh o v rn luyn, lp lp thanh nin  pht huy mnh m truyn thng ca cha ng, n lc phn u, vt mi kh khn, th thch, thc hin xut sc nhim v c giao, gp phn cng ton ng, ton dn v ton qun hon thnh s nghip u tranh gii phng dn tc, thng nht t nc v ngy nay ang chung tay tin hnh cng cuc i mi, xy dng v bo v T quc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Cc phong tro hnh ng cch mng ca tui tr: ''Cm t cho T quc quyt sinh'', ''Tng qun git gic lp cng'', ''Ba sn sng'', ''Nm xung phong'' trong cc cuc khng chin trng k v: ''Thanh nin lp nghip'', ''Tui tr gi nc'', ''Thanh nin tnh nguyn'', ''5 xung kch pht trin kinh t x hi v bo v T quc'', ''4 ng hnh vi thanh nin lp thn, lp nghip''... trong cng cuc i mi, xy dng t nc, v nhng tm gng dng cm qun mnh trong chin u, sng to trong lao ng sn xut, cng tc, hc tp lun ta sng, gp phn t thm thm truyn thng v vang ca on.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Qua cc giai on cch mng, on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh  t chc, tp hp, on kt thanh nin, chm sc, gio dc thiu nin, nhi ng; tch cc tham gia xy dng ng v h thng chnh tr.  c hng triu thanh nin tin tin ng vo hng ng ca on, hng vn on vin u t c kt np vo ng. i ng cn b on ngy cng trng thnh, tr thnh ngun cn b tr di do ca ng, chnh quyn v on th  cc cp.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Vi nhng cng hin xut sc trong 80 nm qua, on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh v tui tr Vit Nam  c ng, Nh nc tng thng Hun chng Sao Vng v nhiu phn thng cao qu khc; v hm nay c tng thng Hun chng Sao Vng ln th 2; iu  th hin s ghi nhn, nh gi cao ca ng, Nh nc v nhn dn i vi nhng thnh tu ca th h tr nc ta v s tin b ca on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Thay mt lnh o ng v Nh nc, ti nhit lit chc mng on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh v biu dng, khen ngi s n lc phn u, ng gp to ln ca cc th h cn b, on vin, thanh nin, thiu nin, nhi ng trong c nc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tha cc ng ch v cc bn,</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">ng, Nh nc v nhn dn ta lun gi trn nim tin yu vo th h tr - nhng ngi ch tng lai ca nc nh, rng ct ca dn tc, lc lng xung kch sng to trong s nghip xy dng v bo v T quc. ng ta v Bc H  nhiu ln khng nh: Thanh nin l tng lai ca chng ta, l hy vng ca chng ta; nc nh thnh hay suy, yu hay mnh phn ln l do cc thanh nin.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Ngh quyt i hi XI ca ng  ch r: ''Lm tt cng tc gio dc chnh tr, t tng, truyn thng, l tng, o c v li sng; to iu kin hc tp, lao ng, gii tr, pht trin ton din th lc, tr tu cho th h tr. Khuyn khch, c v thanh nin nui dng c m, hoi bo ln, xung kch sng to, lm ch khoa hc, cng ngh hin i. Hnh thnh lp thanh nin u t trn mi lnh vc, k tc trung thnh, xut sc s nghip cch mng ca ng, ca dn tc,...''.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> bin Ngh quyt ca ng thnh hnh ng cch mng c th trong phong tro thanh nin, ti  ngh cc ng ch quan tm mt s vn  sau y:</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Mt l, lun lun coi trng cng tc gio dc chnh tr, t tng, vn ha trong thanh nin, gp phn tch cc o to, bi dng th h tr c  phm cht, nng lc lm nhim v xung kch, sng to, k tc s nghip v vang ca ng, thc hin cng nghip ha, hin i ha v mc tiu dn giu, nc mnh, dn ch, cng bng, vn minh, tng bc tin ln ch ngha x hi.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Mun vy, phi i mi v m rng cc hnh thc sinh hot, hc tp, khng ngng bi dng nng cao nhn thc l lun, qun trit ng li nhim v cch mng cho on vin, thanh nin, xy dng bn lnh chnh tr, cng c nim tin, xc nh r trch nhim ca thanh nin trc yu cu v nhim v ca t nc, nng cao lng yu nc, yu ch ngha x hi, tinh thn t lc, t cng,  ch xy dng t nc ngy cng giu mnh, phn vinh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tip tc y mnh Cuc vn ng ''Hc tp v lm theo tm gng o c H Ch Minh'', ''Tui tr Vit Nam hc tp v lm theo li Bc'', tch cc xy dng cc in hnh tin tin  ng o thanh nin, thiu nhi hc tp, noi theo; i u trong xy dng li sng lnh mnh, kin quyt u tranh chng cc biu hin tiu cc, ch ngha c nhn, c hi, thc dng, ch k; xng ng l t chc thanh nin cng sn c mang tn Ch tch H Ch Minh - Anh hng gii phng dn tc, danh nhn vn ha th gii.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Hai l, gn cc hot ng ca on, ca i vi cc nhim v chung ca t nc, nht l tham gia lao ng, xy dng pht trin kinh t, vn ha, gi vng n nh chnh tr x hi; cng c quc phng, an ninh. on cn c nhiu hnh thc hot ng phong ph, a dng, ph hp vi tui tr, li cun thanh nin tham gia tch cc cc phong tro cch mng, nht l trn cc lnh vc, cc a bn c nhiu gian kh, kh khn, th hin r vai tr xung kch theo tinh thn ''u cn thanh nin c, vic g kh c thanh nin''.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Thng xuyn quan tm chm lo i sng vt cht v tinh thn ca on vin, thanh nin; lm tt c ''bi dng'' v ''pht huy''  hot ng ca on ng hng, thit thc, t chc, ng vin c ng o cc tng lp thanh nin.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Ba l, t chc hc tp, qun trit su sc Ngh quyt i hi ln th XI ca ng, trn c s , nghin cu, xy dng chng trnh hnh ng c th, thit thc, trin khai a Ngh quyt i hi vo cuc sng. Thng xuyn quan tm pht trin ngun nhn lc tr, nh hng cho thanh nin hc tp v cc mt, tin cng v lm ch khoa hc - cng ngh, nghip v qun l, rn luyn tay ngh  lm giu cho t nc, cho gia nh v bn thn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">on phi l cu ni quan trng gia thanh nin vi ng v Nh nc, thc y thc hin cc ch trng ca ng, chnh sch, php lut ca Nh nc, to iu kin  thanh nin hot ng trong mt mi trng chnh tr, x hi lnh mnh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Bn l, xy dng on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh v cc t chc ca thanh nin vng mnh ton din,  sc m nhn vai tr nng ct trong phong tro thanh nin v cc hi thanh nin, sinh vin.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">M rng mt trn on kt, tp hp thanh nin Vit Nam c trong nc v  nc ngoi bng nhiu hnh thc a dng, phong ph, khc phc mt s hot ng cn mang tnh hnh thc, hnh chnh ha trong cng tc on. Ch trng nng cao cht lng on vin, nht l cht lng chnh tr, t tng v tnh tin phong, gng mu.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">T chc on cn quan tm y  v ch ng quy hoch, o to, bi dng, s dng v lun chuyn cn b on, rn luyn v la chn nhng cn b on u t, c  phm cht v nng lc  gii thiu ngun cn b cho ng, Nh nc, Mt trn T quc v cc on th.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Nm l, trn c s nhn thc r hn v thi i, v tnh hnh th gii v chnh sch i ngoi ca ng v Nh nc ta, on cn m rng cc hot ng i ngoi ca mnh, gp phn i mi cng tc i ngoi nhn dn, tng cng s hiu bit, on kt vi cc t chc thanh nin cc nc trong khu vc v trn th gii.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tha cc ng ch,</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> o to, bi dng mt th h thanh nin mi, pht trin ton din, k tc trung thnh v xut sc s nghip cch mng ca ng, ca dn tc, cc cp y ng v chnh quyn cn thng xuyn quan tm hn na n cng tc thanh nin v xy dng on Thanh nin, tip tc lnh o, ch o thc hin tt Ngh quyt Trung ng 7 (kha X) v tng cng s lnh o ca ng i vi cng tc thanh nin trong thi k y mnh cng nghip ha, hin i ha t nc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Nm 2011 c ng v Nh nc xc nh l Nm Thanh nin; Ban B th Trung ng ng  c  n v Nm Thanh nin. Cc cp y ng, chnh quyn, on th cn xy dng chng trnh, k hoch hnh ng c th   n v Nm Thanh nin c thc hin c hiu qu. Cc cp b on trn c s xc nh r yu cu, nhim v ca Nm Thanh nin, cn n lc phn u, to bc chuyn bin r rt trong hot ng, to sc sng mi, kh th mi trong hc tp, pht trin kinh t, x hi, khoa hc, cng ngh, bo v mi trng...</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Tha cc ng ch v cc bn,</span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Vi b dy 80 nm xy dng, pht trin, cng hin v trng thnh, on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh  lm nn truyn thng v vang, gp phn lm rng r dn tc ta, nhn dn ta, T quc ta.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Cc th h cha anh  khng tic mu xng  ginh c lp, t do cho T quc,  t nc ta c c c  nh ngy nay. ng, Nh nc v nhn dn lun nh gi cao cng lao to ln ca thanh nin Vit Nam qua cc thi k cch mng v dnh s quan tm c bit i vi th h tr.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">ng thi tin tng rng, vi nhit huyt trn y, vi ngh lc v  ch vn ln mnh m, li ang c sng trong mi trng ha bnh, i mi, pht trin ca t nc, tui tr Vit Nam s lm ht sc mnh, gp phn cng ton ng, ton qun v ton dn gi vng cc thnh qu cch mng, thc hin bng c mc tiu cao c: xy dng T quc ta ngy cng hng cng, t nc ta ngy cng giu mnh, snh vai vi cc cng quc nm chu, nh Bc H hng mong c. Nu khng lm c nh vy l h thn vi lch s, l vong n bi ngha vi cha ng chng ta.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Ti  ngh tui tr Vit Nam  mi min T quc v  nc ngoi hy cng nhau rn c, luyn ti, pht huy truyn thng tt p ca dn tc, ra sc hc tp, rn luyn, tip thu tinh hoa vn ha, khoa hc, cng ngh hin i ca nhn loi  tr thnh mt lp ngi mi, mt ngun nhn lc c tri thc, cht lng cao, cng hin xy dng t nc ta pht trin nhanh v bn vng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">on Thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh tip tc ng vai tr l ht nhn chnh tr, nng ct trong phong tro thanh nin, xng ng l trng hc x hi ch ngha ca thanh nin, i d b tin cy ca ng Cng sn Vit Nam, xung kch i u trong s nghip y mnh cng nghip ha, hin i ha, xy dng v bo v T quc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Mt ln na, chc cc v i biu, cng ton th cc ng ch v cc bn sc khe, hnh phc v thnh cng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><em><span style="font-family: Arial;">Xin trn trng cm n.</span></em></span></p>', 1, 6, 0, 24, '2011-11-15 04:13:47', 62, '', '2011-11-15 09:24:26', 62, 62, '2011-11-17 05:58:07', '2011-11-15 04:13:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 6, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 35, 'robots=\nauthor=');
